content: That's really helpful! I think I'll start by dividing my journal into sections and including daily entries, memorabilia, and photos. I also like the idea of adding interactive elements like flaps and pockets. Since I recently got back from Japan, I still have some of the memorabilia like ticket stubs and brochures, so I'll definitely include those. By the way, I realized I forgot to mention that I returned from Japan on March 20th - I'm still getting used to being back home!
